                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18381126-163-offence-1 t18381126-cd-143"></join>28th of November</rs> 1 shawl, value 7<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18381126-name-965" type="victimName">
